{
  "page": "Cleon the Second",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> King</span><br />Cleon<br /><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> the Second</span></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/King_of_Astapor\" title=\"King of Astapor\">King of Astapor</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Astapor\" title=\"Astapor\">Astapori</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/300_AC\" title=\"300 AC\">300&#160;AC</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Astapor\" title=\"Astapor\">Astapor</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Lover</th><td>\n\"<a href=\"/index.php/Queen_Whore\" title=\"Queen Whore\">Queen Whore</a>\"</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Cleon the Second</b> was the brief <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_Astapor\" title=\"King of Astapor\">King of Astapor</a>, succeeding the first <a href=\"/index.php/Cleon\" title=\"Cleon\">Cleon</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Cleon_the_Second&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Cleon_the_Second&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Cleon succeeds <a href=\"/index.php/Cleon\" title=\"Cleon\">the Butcher King</a> as ruler of <a href=\"/index.php/Astapor\" title=\"Astapor\">Astapor</a>, after the latter's death.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> His reign lasts eight days, before his throat is cut. His killer claims Cleon's throne, and quickly becomes known as <a href=\"/index.php/King_Cutthroat\" title=\"King Cutthroat\">King Cutthroat</a>. At the same time, Cleon's concubine, who becomes known as <a href=\"/index.php/Queen_Whore\" title=\"Queen Whore\">Queen Whore</a>, also claims his crown.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Cleon_the_Second&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd25.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"